Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.shuffletter.iface

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ShuffletterModel
    The interface describing the behavior of a Shuffletter game model.
    ShuffletterModelListener
    An interface implemented by any class used to capture events from a Shuffletter model.
    ShuffletterTile
    A simple interface describing the behavior of a Shuffletter game tile.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NoOpShuffletterModelListener
    An implementation of the ShuffletterModelListener interface which takes no action on any of the methods.
    Position
    A class representing positions on the playing grid.
    ShuffletterIllegalMoveEvent
    A class describing Shuffletter events for illegal moves.
    ShuffletterTileMovedEvent
    A class describing Shuffletter events for tile movement.
    ShuffletterTilePlayedEvent
    A class describing Shuffletter events for tile plays.
